ËIN LOVING MEMORY OF
ANTHONY JOSEPH JOYCE
WE MISS HIS SMILE, HIS CHEERY WAY,
WE MISS THE THINGS HE USED TO SAY,
AND WHEN OLD TIMES WE OFTEN RECALL,
IT'S THEN WE MISS HIM MOST OF ALL.
17.04.1987 - 27.06.2020"▄
